resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group.

load_balancer_name.description: The name of the load balancer.

subscription_id.description: The subscription credentials which uniquely identify the Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

name.description: Gets name of the resource that is unique within the set of probes used by the load balancer. This name can be used to access the resource.

etag.description: A unique read-only string that changes whenever the resource is updated.
